It's a reusable icon library for drawing AWS cloud-architecture diagrams in yEd.

Keybase.pub was a public web-hosting service provided by Keybase that automatically served static files straight out of a user's public cryptographic directory.The service allowed anyone to view or download static files (like HTML web pages, images, text files, or code) over standard HTTPS simply by visiting https://keybase.pub. However, please note that Keybase.pub was officially shut down in March 2023.
